## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c424d-290"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A>сначала выполняет поиск с учетом регистра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c424d-290"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> performs a case-sensitive lookup first.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c424d-291">В случае сбоя выполняется второй Поиск без учета регистра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c424d-291">If it fails, a second case-insensitive search is made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c424d-292">Метод создает `IndexOutOfRange` исключение, если порядковый номер столбца, начинающийся с нуля, не найден.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c424d-292">The method throws an `IndexOutOfRange` exception if the zero-based column ordinal is not found.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c424d-293"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A>не учитывается ширина японской азбуки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c424d-293"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> is kana-width insensitive.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c424d-294">Поскольку уточняющие запросы более эффективны, чем имена уточняющих запросов, вызов <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> в цикле неэффективен.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c424d-294">Because ordinal-based lookups are more efficient than named lookups, it is inefficient to call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> within a loop.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c424d-295">Вместо этого вызовите <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> один раз и затем присвойте результаты целочисленной переменной для использования в цикле.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c424d-295">Instead, call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> once and then assign the results to an integer variable for use within the loop.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c424d-296">В следующем примере показано использование метода <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c424d-296">The following example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub ReadOracleData(ByVal connectionString As String)  
  
    Dim queryString As String = "SELECT OrderID, CustomerID FROM Orders"  
    Dim connection As New OracleConnection(connectionString)  
    Dim command As New OracleCommand(queryString, connectionString)  
  
    connection.Open()  
  
    Dim reader As OracleDataReader = command.ExecuteReader()  
  
    Dim custIdCol As Integer = reader.GetOrdinal("CustomerID")  
  
    Do While reader.Read()  
        Console.WriteLine("CustomerID = {0}", reader.GetString(custIdCol))  
    Loop  
  
    reader.Close()  
    connection.Close()  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void ReadOracleData(string connectionString)  
{  
    string queryString = "SELECT OrderID, CustomerID FROM Orders";  
    OracleConnection connection = new OracleConnection(connectionString);  
    OracleCommand command = new OracleCommand(queryString,connection);  
  
    connection.Open();  
    OracleDataReader reader = command.ExecuteReader();  
  
    int custIdCol = reader.GetOrdinal("CustomerID");  
  
    while (reader.Read())  
        Console.WriteLine("CustomerID = {0}", reader.GetString(custIdCol));  
  
    reader.Close();  
    connection.Close();  
}  
```
